description:
The Saw movie franchise was presumably moving ahead after the success of Saw X. After all, there was once a time when Saw movies were pushed out every year from 2004 to 2010. Sadly, the production of Saw 11 has reportedly been canceled. The eleventh entry in the Saw series was announced in December 2023. [...]

The post ‘Saw 11’ Has Reportedly Been Canceled appeared first on ScreenGeek.
title: ‘Saw 11’ Has Reportedly Been Canceled
